number of reference genes in the category (C), number of genes in the gene set and also in the category (O), expected number in the
category (E), Ratio of enrichment (R), p value from hypergeometric test (rawP), and p value adjusted by the multiple test adjustment (adjP).
Finally, genes in the category are listed. For each gene, the table lists the user uploaded ID and value (optional), Entrez ID,
Ensembl Gene Stable ID, Gene symbol, and description.
